mostly depends on if you have a Rwd or Fwd car and if you only use your car for city driving or country driving

if you have a fwd and use it for city driving you can use the tires you want, NO need for nails (i drove on my summer tires last winter, fwd car)

id consider winter tires (dosen't have to be nails) if you drive a lot out of the city and have a rwd car
